Package org.jcvi.jillion.internal.trace.chromat.scf.section Description

An SCF file is divided into several sections; each section contains only certain fields of a Chromatogram. Each Section is formatted differently and some sections are even formatted differently depending on the specification version. Therefore, Section specific encoders and decoders are needed to handle each Section.

dkatzel
